Package: trelliscope
Title: Create Interactive Trelliscope Displays
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Ryan", "Hafen", , "rhafen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5516-8367"))
Description: Trelliscope is a scalable, flexible, interactive approach to visualizing data. This package provides methods that make it easy to create and interact with Trelliscope displays. High-level functions are provided for creating displays from within 'tidyverse' or 'ggplot2' workflows. Low-level functions are also provided for creating new interfaces.
